      "content": "look i'm just saying, i've seen a lot of people on reddit say that st johns wort is basically just like a natural version of zoloft and that it works the same way. if i just cut my dose in half for a week and then start the supplement at the same time, would that help bridge the gap? it feels like a lot of drama for just changing a pill for a plant.",
